C     OF EXP((0,1)*L*PHI) TIMES THE (N,L) TERM
C     IN THE EXPANSION IN SPHERICAL
C     HARMONICS OF THE FIELD AT LEVEL K,
C     WHERE PHI IS THE AZIMUTHAL ANGLE
C
      TERM(I,N,L,K) = QLN(OFFSET(N,L)+I)*FLN(OFFSET(N,L)+I,K)
C
