C         CO2M58   =  SAME AS CO2M51,WITH P(SFC)= ^810 MB
C         CDTM51   =  FIRST TEMPERATURE DERIVATIVE OF CO2M51
C         CDTM58   =  FIRST TEMPERATURE DERIVATIVE OF CO2M58
C         C2DM51   =  SECOND TEMPERATURE DERIVATIVE OF CO2M51
