C         GTEMP    =  WEIGHTING FUNCTION FOR MODEL PRESSURE LEVEL
C                        STRUCTURE WITH P(SFC)=1013.25 MB.
C         B0       =  TEMP. COEFFICIENT USED FOR CO2 TRANS. FCTN.
