      COMMON / BDWIDE / AWIDE,BWIDE,BETAWD,
     1                  APWD,BPWD,ATPWD,BTPWD,
     2                  BDLOWD,BDHIWD,BETINW,
     3                  AB15WD,SKO2D,SKC1R,SKO3R
