      SUBROUTINE GETDIA(J,L,A)
C  GET DIAGNOSTICS FROM DISK OR MEMORY
C  CALL SYNDIA OR ANOTHER GETDIA OR PUTDIA TO FINISH I/O
C
C  J IS RECORD NUMBER
C  L IS RECORD LENGTH
C  A IS ARRAY OF LENGTH L TO GET
C
