C-DG3 ENDDO
C-DG3 CALL ROWSEP(WORK)
C-DG3 LBM=SLMSEP.GT.0.
C-DG3 CALL GRIBIT(WORK,LBM,4,LONB,LATB,16,COLRAB,28,2,ICEN,IGEN,
