C-DG3&            IFTIME,ITHR,0,INST,0,0,ICEN2,IDS(ITEMP),IENS,
C-DG3&            0.,0.,0.,0.,0.,0.,G,LG,IERR)
C-DG3 IF(IERR.EQ.0) CALL WRYTE(NDG,LG,G)
